```plantuml
@startuml sfujiwara_terraform-google-ai-platform-notification

actor User as U
participant "Google Cloud Logging" as GCL
participant "Logging Sink" as LS
participant "Pub/Sub Topic (ai_platform_log)" as PST
participant "Cloud Function" as CF
participant "Pub/Sub Topic (notification)" as PSN

U -> GCL: Starts AI Platform Job
GCL -> LS: Generates Log Entry
LS -> PST: Forwards Log Entry

PST -> CF: Sends Log Message
CF -> CF: Processes Log Message
CF -> CF: Detects Job State Change

CF -> PSN: Publishes Notification
PSN -> U: Receives Notification

@enduml
```